        "created_at": "2025-10-25T17:25:27.281Z",
        "cooked": "<p>This is already requested in several forms:</p>\n<aside class=\"quote\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"28706\">\n  <div class=\"title\">\n    <div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n    <img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/a/4da419/48.png\" class=\"avatar\">\n    <div class=\"quote-title__text-content\">\n      <a href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/t/2fa-token-and-security-key-compatibility/28706\">2FA (Token and Security Key) Compatibility</a> <a class=\"badge-category__wrapper \" href=\"/c/feature-requests/17\"><span data-category-id=\"17\" style=\"--category-badge-color: #83B72A; --category-badge-text-color: #FFFFFF;\" data-drop-close=\"true\" class=\"badge-category --style-square \" title=\"Post your ideas here for new features and functionality for the Signal app.\"><span class=\"badge-category__name\">Feature Requests</span></span></a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <blockquote>\n    Please add 2FA token compatibility such as ‚ÄúAuthy‚Äù etc as well as security key like ‚ÄúYubikey‚Äù in your next update. These are more secure. Thank-you.\n  </blockquote>\n</aside>\n\n<aside class=\"quote\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"53172\">\n  <div class=\"title\">\n    <div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n    <img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/avitus/48/34172_2.png\" class=\"avatar\">\n    <div class=\"quote-title__text-content\">\n      <a href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/t/implement-passkeys/53172\">Implement passkeys</a> <a class=\"badge-category__wrapper \" href=\"/c/feature-requests/17\"><span data-category-id=\"17\" style=\"--category-badge-color: #83B72A; --category-badge-text-color: #FFFFFF;\" data-drop-close=\"true\" class=\"badge-category --style-square \" title=\"Post your ideas here for new features and functionality for the Signal app.\"><span class=\"badge-category__name\">Feature Requests</span></span></a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <blockquote>\n    Passkeys are starting to get rolled out by Google, Apple, and Microsoft. It would be a massive security boost to implement this new standard (likely to work with a future cloud backup option).\n  </blockquote>\n</aside>\n\n<p>Also just calling out the opening post appears to be AI-generated, so a quick reminder:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<h4>Forum policy: Generative AI</h4>\n<p>In the spirit of preserving human interactions on this forum, generative artificial intelligence (GenAI) and large language model (LLM) usage (such as using OpenAI ChatGPT, Google Gemini, DeepSeek, and any similar tools, including self-hosted models) is strictly forbidden to generate text, images, videos, and any other form of content.</p>\n<p>Posts showing signs of being machine generated in this way may be removed without notice, and user activity may be restricted, at the moderation team‚Äôs discretion.</p>\n<p>Please note that using automated tools to aid in translation of human-authored text (such as LibreTranslate, Google Translate, and DeepL) remains allowed.</p>\n<p>Thank you for understanding,</p>\n<p>Your volunteer moderation team</p>\n</blockquote>",
